http://www.itcompany.com/regdoctor.htm&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.itcompany.com/regdoctor.htm&lt;/a&gt;



The Portable SFX EXE file is built up using WinRAR. You can use it to extract the files and check them one by one if you want to be sure of what is running on your machine.


This also has been built up on an XP x86 machine, I don't know if this program can run on a x64 or Vista/W7 machine. It's up to you to check it if you are using them.



